Mailbox MCB. More...

#include <drivers/mailbox/include/mailbox_internal.h>

Data Fields

uint8_t initFlag
 Flag that checks if the Driver has been initialized. It can be initialized only once per master (DSS or MSS).
 
Mailbox_Type localEndpoint
 Stores the local endpoint which must be the same across all instances of the driver for a given master.
 
uint8_t bssInstCount
 Assures that only one instance of the driver is open (for this master) to the BSS.
 
uint8_t mssDssInstCount
 Counts the number of MSS<->DSS instances of the driver (for this master).
 
uint8_t mssDssReadChIDInUse
 Stores status of read channel. Used to prevent multiple instances of MSS-DSS mailbox to use the channel at the same time.
 
uint8_t mssDssWriteChIDInUse
 Stores status of write channel. Used to prevent multiple instances of MSS-DSS mailbox to use the channel at the same time.
 
Mailbox_ChType mssDssChType
 Indicates if multichannel is enabled between MSS<->DSS. All mailbox instances between MSS and DSS must have the same channel type configuration.
 
Mbox_Handle lastMsgSentHandle
 Stores the handle of the driver instance for the last message that was sent. Used during ISR to determine which driver received the acknowledgement as ISR is received without message. Used in extended mode for MSS<->DSS communication only.
 
Mailbox_HwCfg * mssDssHwCfgPtr
 Stores a pointer for the hardware configuration used by the MSS<->DSS communication.
 
Mailbox_HwiHandles_t hwiHandles
 Registered Mailbox Interrupt Handlers.
 
Mailbox_ISRErrorCnt_t errCnt
 Store ISR error conditions.
 
Mbox_Handle handleArray [MAILBOX_CH_ID_MAX+1]
 Array that stores handles for all mailbox instances. Used in extended mode for MSS<->DSS communication only.
